{"tid":763431,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[屌撚醒你地系列]曖昧？姐係唔夠鐘意呀！","createTime":"2018-08-01T06:11:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T07:53:34.000Z","uid":139763,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f443456df04afdbc764d1b3f549e5eacaeef5dbf","tid":763431,"uid":139763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T06:11:23.000Z","msg":"你以為你地而家曖昧好開心？<br />\n無錯，通常會曖昧都係源於彼此有好感<br />\n（收兵嗰啲仆街就除外啦）<br />\n但如果你地曖昧咗一段好長時間<br />\n長撚到你唔知自己做緊咩<br />\n心諗點解仲行唔到去嗰步既時候<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 屌！其實呢，佢根本唔係咁鐘意你呀！</span></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">懵！撚！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n不過呢！又畀佢吹脹喎，<br />\n因為你否定唔到佢真係完全對你無好感<br />\n佢都有投放時間落你度<br />\n<br />\n但！<br />\n你又肯定唔到佢真係鐘意你喎<br />\n因為如果係鐘意你<br />\n你地就一早一齊咗啦<br />\n洗上連登睇post自我安慰咩<br />\n<br />\n佢一直咁拖<br />\n係因為佢好享受呢個過程<br />\n佢知你對佢有好感<br />\n甚至feel到你鐘意佢<br />\n但係佢就遲遲唔踏出嗰一步<br />\n點解？<br />\n可能佢根本就大撚把曖昧對象<br />\n或 佢有更鐘意既人<br />\n或 你唔係真係吸引到佢要非同你一齊不可<br />\n<br />\n邊有人會唔鐘意自己比人鐘意架？<br />\n佢唔似你咁戇鳩<br />\n邊有咁蠢放你走<br />\n所以咪拖得就拖囉<br />\n明未呀！？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 結論</span><br />\n係真心鐘意你既<br />\n唔會曖昧好耐<br />\n曖昧未必係好事<br />\n比個期限自己<br />\n到期都係無進展既<br />\n你就自動收皮喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e2d24ff8d8fb108728756aeb27cc09247179485","tid":763431,"uid":148185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T06:14:00.000Z","msg":"too long"},{"pid":"8dc833d568822b45b4974f840ada1b772f952ce8","tid":763431,"uid":139763,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"0e2d24ff8d8fb108728756aeb27cc09247179485","tid":763431,"uid":148185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T06:14:00.000Z","msg":"too long"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T06:15:39.000Z","msg":"咁你咪唔好睇囉"},{"pid":"d145bca876fdf4a4e633370adad3f545f431d37b","tid":763431,"uid":17426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T06:16:32.000Z","msg":"點樣為止曖昧 我都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b148bd9224330e3c231241d75dec7e98e60f1309","tid":763431,"uid":146514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d145bca876fdf4a4e633370adad3f545f431d37b","tid":763431,"uid":17426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T06:16:32.000Z","msg":"點樣為止曖昧 我都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T06:18:15.000Z","msg":"唔好暗戀&hellip;"},{"pid":"1ebe34ea6bab8360d64212df07a03c6f7b0bbf3f","tid":763431,"uid":179971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T06:41:01.000Z","msg":"好中...會有報應架..."},{"pid":"0ed26925e08eed070925ef440f453ba9e7e40b0d","tid":763431,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T07:00:55.000Z","msg":"限期應該比幾耐？"},{"pid":"cff9413aa8830fcaa7b04b8955f0a4bfe066810f","tid":763431,"uid":195431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T07:05:43.000Z","msg":"睇黎你俾拒絕左..."},{"pid":"c20da886fb4733083c82ba2f1a7e318ece08b3f0","tid":763431,"uid":148692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T07:11:49.000Z","msg":"鬼叫你係做主動或者鍾意人先咩"},{"pid":"8e5d596c77d8b2b44c7cea72b414062dbb9f78e4","tid":763431,"uid":139763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d145bca876fdf4a4e633370adad3f545f431d37b","tid":763431,"uid":17426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T06:16:32.000Z","msg":"點樣為止曖昧 我都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T07:52:01.000Z","msg":"做啲野講啲野好似情侶<br />\n但又唔係情侶<br />\n友達以上 戀人未滿"},{"pid":"560b541f31d6e545d143a7d8dafccf0d56de2979","tid":763431,"uid":139763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ed26925e08eed070925ef440f453ba9e7e40b0d","tid":763431,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T07:00:55.000Z","msg":"限期應該比幾耐？"},"citedB